reviews.review_text: Let it Grow This source sounds great. Check out Let it Grow..unreal..Phil is killing it.
Who woulda thunk For two gens, this sounds very good. Well worth the download. Thanks.

Thanks a-lot! This is the best aud source imho. I really enjoy this Help>Slip>Franklin's too. Something is seems different about Shakedown Street, and I can't put my finger on it.  Thanks again for the source!
Pretty good playing, shaky vocals & an unexciting setlist. I like this recording best of all currently available.
